    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>You&rsquo;re trained in fighting opponents that are larger than you, and you are skilled at keeping them on their toes, pestering them from all directions.</p></em>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelType\">You gain a +1 trait bonus on Acrobatics checks, and Acrobatics becomes a class skill for you. In addition, you gain a +4 trait bonus on Acrobatics checks to move through an enemy&rsquo;s space without provoking an attack of opportunity, provided that enemy is larger than you.</span></p>",
